            challenging black runs, this area caters to all abilities. The famous "Le Br√©vent"
            summit at 2,525m offers panoramic views that are simply unforgettable.
          </p>
          <ul class="ski-stats">
            <li>Altitude: 1,035m ‚Äì 2,525m</li>
            <li>Runs: 44 pistes</li>
            <li>Lifts: 24</li>
