            <li>Runs: 21 pistes</li>
            <li>Best for: Beginners & families</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="ski-area-card">
          <h3>Aiguille du Midi</h3>
          <p class="ski-distance">5 minutes from town centre</p>
          <p>
            The legendary Vall√©e Blanche off-piste route descends 24km from 3,842m through
            glacial landscapes. An unmissable experience for any serious skier visiting Chamonix.
          </p>
          <ul class="ski-stats">
            <li>Altitude: 3,842m summit</li>
            <li>Vall√©e Blanche: 24km</li>
            <li>Best for: Guided off-piste</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Dining Section -->
  <section class="section-spacing">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Dining & Apr√®s-Ski</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          From mountain refuges to Michelin-starred cuisine
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="dining-grid">
        <div class="dining-category">
          <h3>Fine Dining</h3>
          <ul class="dining-list">
            <li>
              <strong>Albert 1er</strong>
