            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="dining-category">
          <h3>Apr√®s-Ski</h3>
          <ul class="dining-list">
            <li>
              <strong>Bar'd Up</strong>
              <span>Legendary apr√®s-ski venue with live music and a lively atmosphere</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Monkey Bar</strong>
              <span>Popular apr√®s spot with great cocktails and a buzzing crowd</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Elevation 1904</strong>
              <span>Sophisticated bar with an excellent selection of wines and spirits</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="dining-category">
          <h3>Casual & Family</h3>
          <ul class="dining-list">
            <li>
