        </div>

        <div class="activity-card">
          <div class="activity-icon">üõÅ</div>
          <h3>Spa & Wellness</h3>
          <p>Relax at Chamonix's excellent spa facilities, or unwind in Chalet Josephine's private hot tub and sauna after a day of adventure in the mountains.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Practical Info -->
  <section class="section-spacing">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-12">Getting Here</h2>
      <div class="travel-grid">
        <div class="travel-card">
          <h3>‚úàÔ∏è By Air</h3>
          <p>Geneva Airport is the closest international hub, just 90 minutes from Chamonix. We can arrange private airport transfers directly to your door.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Geneva (GVA): 90 min</li>
            <li>Lyon (LYS): 2.5 hours</li>
            <li>Paris (CDG): 5 hours</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="travel-card">
          <h3>üöÇ By Train</h3>
          <p>Direct trains run from Geneva to Chamonix via the scenic Mont-Blanc Express route. A beautiful journey through the Alps.</p>
